CBRE Hotels has been exclusively retained to market for sale the Westend Hotel, Sydney.

Currently operated under management as a backpacker hotel, the property features:

 Sydney freehold hotel with vacant possession potential
 86 rooms in total over 13 floors, currently  operating as 359-bed backpacker hotel under the Nomads brand
 Southern CBD location, close to Central Station, World Square, UTS University
 Strong consistent income with scope for improvement
 Huge scope for refurbishment, repositioning, revenue enhancement
 Rare opportunity to secure a Sydney CBD freehold accommodation asset with VP


For Sale by Expressions of Interest closing on Thursday 12th March 2015.

CBRE are delighted to present this rare lifestyle and corporate investment opportunity situated opposite Barangaroo Central.This is a rare chance to own a unique office or retail property on the doorstep of Australia's largest mixed-use waterfront development.
Located on the doorstep of Barangaroo, 36 The Bond is located at 36 Hickson Road, Sydney's hottest inner-urban precinct. The 22-hectare Barangaroo development combines prestige residential, hotel, retail, and office space with open parkland and cultural assets including a museum and theatres - a truly unique harbourside offering. A magnet for prestige Australian and international corporations, the precinct is fast developing into one of the country's most creative enclaves. Leading advertising agencies, media and design companies already operating in the area include Yahoo!7, Hassell, Sydney Theatre Company, Mojo, Leo Burnett and Universal Music. Barangaroo South has secured the commitment of mainstream corporates, including KPMG, Westpac, Lend Lease and PWC.

• Top Floor 254sqm office spanning across two storeys
• Uninterrupted views of Sydney's Harbour from every angle
• Ideal for owner occupiers or investors
• Abundance of natural light with full height windows, skylights, open air winter garden
• Striking creative warehouse design, exposed beams and double-height pitched ceilings
• One (1) car space included, stair & lift access, internal kitchen and  2 x bathroom facilities including a shower, 24-hour security access, video intercom, air conditioning
• A rare opportunity to acquire a secure, elite investment or your future prime office space shared by distinguished neighbours and the re-development of Barangaroo – this office will always be highly sought after

For sale via Public Auction on the 13th of October 2015.
